subSubSection.paragraph:
Diagnosis
: Characterized by the following combination of characters: head yellow with dark red brown stripes (
Figs 13, 19
), yellow-brown antennal segment I with two red-brown rings (
Fig. 21
), left paramere apical process without a distinct dorsobasal process (
Fig. 35
) and endosoma possessing three sclerites (
Fig. 39
).
